      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "又抽象起来了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "今早情绪有点崩溃，开始胡言乱语了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "看学生提纲，看崩溃了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "那就是一团不可回收垃圾，应该放在不可回收垃圾站",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "算了可能以前我的导师也是这么觉得的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "情绪太跳跃了吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "到底几个意思啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "当老师没有不疯的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得大学老师还好吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有教幼儿园和小学那么崩溃",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "也是",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "教小学生的耐心，我愿称之为超级忍人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "甚至可以养比格",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh比格名声在外",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "说到这个小比",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "小比真的好可爱",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你养...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "让我多活两年吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我并不是什么十恶不赦的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，之前我们聊双男主的时候",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我忘了说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "你看过心之全蚀吗？",
